></item><item><title>极右翼 MK 被任命代表政府参加有争议的司法小组</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mk-tapped-to-represent-government-in-disputed-judicial-panel/0000018b-d787-df9a-ab8b-dfcf75d40000</link><description>宗教犹太复国主义议员奥里特·斯特罗克 (Orit Strock) 在周四的委员会会议之前当选，这是自 2022 年底政府成立以来的第一次会议。司法部长亚里夫·莱文 (Yariv Levin) 在向高等法院提出请愿后决定召开该委员会会议，寻求迫使他这样做所以</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mk-tapped-to-represent-government-in-disputed-judicial-panel/0000018b-d787-df9a-ab8b-dfcf75d40000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀后，十月份寻求枪支许可证的以色列人急剧增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/dramatic-increase-in-israelis-seeking-gun-permits-in-october-following-hamas-massacre/0000018b-d4db-d423-affb-f7fb34610000</link><description>国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔强调公民防卫工作的必要性，敦促任何有资格的人“即使在今天也要这样做”；其他人则警告大规模分发枪支的后果</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:11:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/dramatic-increase-in-israelis-seeking-gun-permits-in-october-following-hamas-massacre/0000018b-d4db-d423-affb-f7fb34610000</guid></item><item><title>屠杀后失踪的12岁女孩的家人放弃希望告别</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/giving-up-hope-family-of-girl-12-missing-since-massacre-say-goodbye/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb37350000</link><description>来自贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri) 的 12 岁女孩 Liel Hetzroni 的家人决定将她的物品埋在尸体的地方。 “莉尔被谋杀的事实很清楚，”一位亲戚在向莉尔告别时说道，莉尔被认为已经死亡，旁边还有她的双胞胎兄弟、阿姨和祖父，他们都于 10 月 7 日被杀。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/giving-up-hope-family-of-girl-12-missing-since-massacre-say-goodbye/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb37350000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷附近检查站发生枪击事件，六名以色列人受伤，其中一人伤势严重；三名枪手被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/6-wounded-1-critically-in-shooting-attack-at-checkpoint-near-jerusalem-3-gunmen-killed/0000018b-d757-d423-affb-f7f7059b0000</link><description>三名袭击者在伯利恒附近西岸的“隧道”检查站向安全部队开枪。警方报告称，他们打算在耶路撒冷境内发动袭击，但被拦截并向驻扎在那里的警察开枪</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/6-wounded-1-critically-in-shooting-attack-at-checkpoint-near-jerusalem-3-gunmen-killed/0000018b-d757-d423-affb-f7f7059b0000</guid></item><item><title>“TikTok 明星”：讲俄语的老年人向以色列战争努力伸出援手</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tiktok-stars-the-russian-speaking-seniors-lending-a-hand-to-the-israeli-war-effort/0000018b-d3dc-df9a-ab8b-dfdc01250000</link><description>20 多年前从前苏联集团移民到以色列的四名妇女解释了为什么她们不能在加沙战争持续时袖手旁​​观，并感到有责任尽其所能提供帮助</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 08:47:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tiktok-stars-the-russian-speaking-seniors-lending-a-hand-to-the-israeli-war-effort/0000018b-d3dc-df9a-ab8b-dfdc01250000</guid></item><item><title>联合国安理会呼吁暂停加沙人道主义行动并无条件释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/un-security-council-calls-for-humanitarian-pauses-unconditional-release-of-hostages/0000018b-d6ee-d168-a3ef-d7fe19b50000</link><description>安理会“软化”了这一呼吁的措辞，该呼吁在之前失败的决议中被视为“要求”。美国、英国和俄罗斯投了弃权票</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 07:56:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/un-security-council-calls-for-humanitarian-pauses-unconditional-release-of-hostages/0000018b-d6ee-d168-a3ef-d7fe19b50000</guid></item><item><title>利库德集团“对内塔尼亚胡感到愤怒”，称“政府的日子已经屈指可数了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/likud-mk-enraged-with-netanyahu-says-governments-days-are-numbered/0000018b-d6db-d423-affb-f7fb86cb0000</link><description>前公共外交部长加利特·迪斯塔尔·阿特巴扬 (Galit Distal Atbaryan) 写道，“我对以色列北部和南部政府统治下崛起的怪物感到愤怒，这让我心碎并让我辞职。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 06:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/likud-mk-enraged-with-netanyahu-says-governments-days-are-numbered/0000018b-d6db-d423-affb-f7fb86cb0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷检查站枪击事件中，六名以色列人受伤，其中一人伤势严重；三名枪手被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-live/biden-war-wont-end-until-hamas-destroyed-un-calls-for-urgent-cease-fire-in-gaza/0000018b-d5f5-df9a-ab8b-dffd41030000</link><description>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的名字 ■ 拜登表示，重新占领加沙将是“一个大错误” ■ 八名以色列人在耶路撒冷检查站枪击事件中受伤，其中一人伤势严重 ■ 联合国安理会呼吁“紧急”停火并无条件释放以色列人人质 ■ 以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩真主党 ■ 巴勒斯坦报道：以色列国防军重新进入希法，进行挖掘 ■ 以色列反对派领袖猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡，提议由另一位利库德集团成员领导新政府 ■ 自 239 年 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀加沙被扣押的人质 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：11,240 人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 04:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-live/biden-war-wont-end-until-hamas-destroyed-un-calls-for-urgent-cease-fire-in-gaza/0000018b-d5f5-df9a-ab8b-dffd41030000</guid></item><item><title>警方在民主党总部逮捕要求加沙停火的示威者后，犹太抗议者与亲以色列议员发生争执</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/jewish-protesters-pro-israel-lawmaker-spar-after-gaza-cease-fire-rally/0000018b-d63e-d168-a3ef-d7fe6ae70000</link><description>国会警察暴力驱散了在民主党国会竞选委员会外参加跨宗教守夜活动和反对以色列加沙战争的公民不服从活动的示威者，要求议员支持停火。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 04:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/jewish-protesters-pro-israel-lawmaker-spar-after-gaza-cease-fire-rally/0000018b-d63e-d168-a3ef-d7fe6ae70000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列来说，对加沙希法医院的袭击是向哈马斯发出的坚定信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/for-israel-the-raid-on-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-is-a-firm-message-for-hamas/0000018b-d4eb-d423-affb-f7eb5c7b0000</link><description>以色列冒着采取复杂策略的风险，增加了与哈马斯核心安全基础设施的接触。以色列国防军希望发出信号，尽管当前的突袭目标有限，但其部队没有害怕进入的地方，也没有哈马斯可以感到安全的地方</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 04:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/for-israel-the-raid-on-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-is-a-firm-message-for-hamas/0000018b-d4eb-d423-affb-f7eb5c7b0000</guid></item><item><title>西方警告以色列：加沙战争损害我们与阿拉伯世界的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/west-warns-israel-gaza-war-harming-our-relations-with-arab-world/0000018b-d4ed-dffa-adef-f6ed91ea0000</link><description>美国和欧洲外交官告诉《国土报》，他们支持以色列对 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击作出反应，这让阿拉伯和穆斯林世界付出了代价 — — 特别是在平民伤亡不断增加以及以色列在医院开展军事行动的情况下</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 03:59:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/west-warns-israel-gaza-war-harming-our-relations-with-arab-world/0000018b-d4ed-dffa-adef-f6ed91ea0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管批评越来越多，拜登坚称以色列战争不会结束，直到哈马斯被彻底摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/despite-growing-criticism-biden-insists-israel-war-wont-end-until-hamas-fully-destroyed/0000018b-d5da-df9a-ab8b-dfda85780000</link><description>由于民主党和他自己的国家机器内部的不满情绪日益高涨，拜登的行动期限比以色列总理更紧迫 — — 更不用说政府试图在不给予太多氧气的情况下承认一场舆论战了</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 02:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/despite-growing-criticism-biden-insists-israel-war-wont-end-until-hamas-fully-destroyed/0000018b-d5da-df9a-ab8b-dfda85780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的下一个惊喜来自约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-next-surprise-is-coming-from-the-west-bank/0000018b-d4d9-df9a-ab8b-ded9c6030000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 00:36:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-next-surprise-is-coming-from-the-west-bank/0000018b-d4d9-df9a-ab8b-ded9c6030000</guid></item><item><title>为什么自由派西方反对以色列？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-the-liberal-west-is-against-israel/0000018b-d4d9-d423-affb-f7fbc57f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 00:23:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-the-liberal-west-is-against-israel/0000018b-d4d9-d423-affb-f7fbc57f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队不是帮派</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-16/ty-article/the-israeli-army-is-not-a-gang/0000018b-d4d9-dffa-adef-f6d9c5820000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 23:20:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-16/ty-article/the-israeli-army-is-not-a-gang/0000018b-d4d9-dffa-adef-f6d9c5820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对派领袖猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡，提议由另一位利库德集团成员领导新政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-slams-netanyahu-proposes-new-govt-led-by-another-likud-member/0000018b-d4fc-dffa-adef-f6fc77570000</link><description>以色列反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德表示，以色列不能允许自己“与我们根本不信任的总理”进行长期军事行动</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 22:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-slams-netanyahu-proposes-new-govt-led-by-another-likud-member/0000018b-d4fc-dffa-adef-f6fc77570000</guid></item><item><title>揭晓：美国为以色列提供加沙战争的弹药</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-16/ty-article/shells-laser-guided-missiles-and-bunker-busters-the-munitions-the-u-s-supplied-israel/0000018b-d3b9-dffa-adef-f7b990750000</link><description>五角大楼内部文件详细介绍了“以色列高级领导人”提出的弹药要求 ■ 国会民主党人对拜登政府缺乏透明度越来越警惕</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 22:05: